quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  18,106,"Sidaas waa in abaalkoodu yahay Jahannama; gaalnimadooda darteed, waxayna ka yeesheen Aayadahayga iyo Rusushayda jeesjees."
  18,107,"Kuwa (Xaqa) rumeeyey ee samaha fala waxay leeyihiin beeraha Al-Firdaws{2} degitaan (marti qaad) ahaan.",footnotes:1:[. Al-Firdaws waa halka ugu sarreysa uguna fiican Jannada.],footnotes:2:[]
  18,108,"Iyagoo ku dhex waaraya weligood mana doonaan inay xaggeeda ka wareegaan (guuraan)."
  19,67,"Miyuusan Aadmigu xusuusnayn inaan abuurnay kal hore isagoon waxba ahayn?"
  19,68,"Ee Rabbigaa baan ku dhaartaye, waanu soo kulmin iyaga iyo shaydaammadaba, markaas waxaanu keeni hareeraha jahannama iyagoo jilba joogsan{2}.",footnotes:1:[. Iyagoo kuf kufaya oo jilbahooda u dhacaya argagax darteed ama loo jiidayo Naarta iyagoo aan dooneyn oo jilbaha ku jooga oo dhulka ku jiidaya.],footnotes:2:[]
  19,69,"Markaas waxaan ka soo siibi qolo walba kuwooda ugu dar-darnaa xagga Raxmaanka (Allaah)."
  20,49,"(Fircoon) wuxuu yidhi: “Waa Kuma Rabbigiin, Muusow?”"
  20,50,"(Muuse) wuxuu yidhi: Rabbigayo waa kan siiyey wax walba qaabka uu leeyahay oo u tilmaamay (yoolkeed).”"
  20,51,"(Fircoon) wuxuu yidhi: “Ka warran xaalka facyadii hore?.”"
  21,25,"Ma aanuna soo dirin hortaa Rasuulna aan u waxyoon (Annagoo leh), "Ma jiro Ilaah (Xaq ah oo) aan Aniga (Allaah) ahayn, ee i caabuda (Anigoo keliya).”"
  21,26,"Waxay (gaaladu) yidhaahdeen: Raxmaanku wuxuu yeeshay ilmo. Subxaanah! Wuu ka hufan yahay, waase addoomo (malaa’igta) la sharfay{2}.",footnotes:1:[. Kuwaa ay ku andoocadaan inay yihiin ilaah sida ruuxul qudus, ama ilmahii Alle sida Ciise, malaa’igta, iwm waa addoommo la sharfay.],footnotes:2:[]
  21,27,"Kagama hormaraan hadal, iyaguna amarkiisa uun bay ku camal falaan."
  22,1,"Dadow! Iska jira (Ciqaabka) Rabbigiin! Hubaal, Gariirka Saacadda (Qiyaame) waa wax weyn oo daran."
  22,2,"Maalintaad arki haweeney kastoo ilmo nuujinaysa iyadoo ka tegi ilmahay naaska nuujinaysay, oo haweeney walboo uur leh dhicin waxay uurka ku siddo, waxaadna arki dadka oo (ah sida kuwo) sakhraansan, mana aha kuwo sakhraansan, Cadaabka Alle baase ah mid Daran."
  22,3,"Waxaa ka mid ah dadka mid ka dooda arrinka Alle cilmi la’aan, raacana Shaydaan kastoo madax adag."
